name: Aquarius Camus
description:
Is the Golden Knight of Aquarius, known as the "Mage of water and ice". 
Camus is apparently a stoic, cold and distant person, since he believes that as a Gold Saint, 
he should never show exasperation or it would draw the people into despair. 
His cold demeanor is not based on suppressing his feelings but instead in controlling them. 
He fights for what he believes is correct and is willing to do anything to defend his ideals. 

#047 Saint Seiya Pack
